title: Taste fresh Queensland Seafood at Gladstone Seafood FestivalTravelandtourworld.com
text:
Taste fresh Queensland Seafood at Gladstone Seafood Festival Published on : Monday, September 21, 2015
The 2015 Gladstone Seafood Festival promises to deliver an abundance of fresh Queensland Seafood, fantastic live music, bar, rides for the kids, cooking demonstrations by their celebrity chef and much more!
It will be held at the beautiful GPC Marina Parklands from 11am to 5pm on October 25.
Experience a tidal wave of tastes, featuring fresh locally sourced seafood at the Gladstone Seafood Festival.
This free family event will include a line up of awesome entertainment. The adults will enjoy cooling off in the licensed bar area with beer, wine and frozen margaritas.
Entry is completely free. Food, drinks and rides can be purchased on the day.
